300.8967, 299.9125, 297.5817, 298.3072, 299.88, 300.3405, 301.0188, 302.4248, 300.0331, 300.6752, 302.3573, 303.1397, 302.2272, 303.4756, 301.3473, 302.426, 302.4427, 303.1032, 299.5772, 296.1362, 297.3221, 298.0985, 296.6362, 297.1246, 298.4914, 298.998, 298.6499, 297.2135, 297.7311, 298.4874, 298.1123, 298.3072, 300.2446, 303.0451, 307.1896, 306.0989, 308.2393, 311.1005, 312.4235, 309.5846, 309.677, 310.0913, 309.9359, 312.4967, 312.4099, 317.7436, 320.5357, 318.4438, 316.4563, 317.4278, 313.4787, 317.1428, 317.4765, 315.5595, 315.4171, 312.4896, 318.2836, 319.0728, 319.7439, 313.7763, 315.6944, 313.4241, 313.6813, 313.1675, 312.7941, 312.1963, 311.7039, 311.2185, 312.2358, 312.3158, 312.3637, 312.434, 312.9426, 313.6015, 313.2918, 313.1624, 311.2584, 309.7956, 308.9446, 308.0824, 308.5233, 308.554, 308.4807, 308.1645, 308.4193, 308.1597], "summary_html": "<h1>Volatility-Momentum Interaction Factor</h1>\n<h2>策略概述</h2>\n<p>基于 GARCH(1,1) 条件波动率的变化率与价格动量方向的交互信号。核心逻辑：当波动率上升（vol_persist_chg &gt; 0）且价格上涨（mom_20 &gt; 0）时做多，波动率上升但价格下跌时做空。即\"波动率放大方向上的动量信号\"。</p>\n<p>信号构建流程： 1. 计算 GARCH(1,1) 条件波动率（252日滚动窗口，每20日重拟合） 2. 波动率持续性变化率：cond_vol(t) / cond_vol(t-20) - 1 3. 20日价格动量方向：sign(close(t) / close(t-20) - 1) 4. 交互信号：vol_persist_chg × sign(momentum) 5. 截面排名 → 连续信号[-1,1] → 波动率目标缩放(15%) → 20日再平衡</p>\n<p>预处理包含 Hurst 指数、已实现波动率、EWMA 波动率、跳跃频率的暖机过滤，确保信号质量。</p>\n<h2>回测表现</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (全期, 4bps)</td><td><strong>1.54</strong></td></tr><tr><td>年化收益</td><td>6.3%</td></tr><tr><td>年化波动</td><td>4.1%</td></tr><tr><td>最大回撤</td><td>-4.6%</td></tr><tr><td>日均换手</td><td>0.11</td></tr><tr><td>回测天数</td><td>3368</td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本内 2016-2025)</td><td><strong>1.65</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本外 2025+)</td><td><strong>1.22</strong></td></tr><tr><td>半样本 H1/H2</td><td>1.68 / 1.63</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>年度 Sharpe</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>年份</th><th>2012</th><th>2013</th><th>2014</th><th>2015</th><th>2016</th><th>2017</th><th>2018</th><th>2019</th><th>2020</th><th>2021</th><th>2022</th><th>2023</th><th>2024</th><th>2025</th><th>2026</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe</td><td>0.48</td><td>1.82</td><td>1.37</td><td>1.52</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">3.02</span></td><td>1.89</td><td>0.22</td><td>0.28</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.73</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.25</span></td><td>1.61</td><td>0.92</td><td>1.54</td><td>1.49</td><td>0.89</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数据字段依赖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>字段</th><th>说明</th><th>必需</th></tr><tr><td><code>close</code></td><td>收盘价</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>open</code></td><td>开盘价</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>high</code></td><td>最高价</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>low</code></td><td>最低价</td><td>是</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>信号更新频率</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>调仓周期</strong>: 每 10 个交易日</li>\n<li><strong>信号更新</strong>: 每日计算，每 10 天生效</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>品种覆盖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>覆盖品种数</td><td>59</td></tr><tr><td>回测交易日</td><td>3370</td></tr><tr><td>非零仓位占比</td><td>98.2%</td></tr><tr><td>日均持仓品种</td><td>40.8</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数学公式</h2>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{vol\\_persist\\_chg}_t = \\frac{\\sigma^{GARCH}_t}{\\sigma^{GARCH}_{t-20}} - 1</div>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{signal}_t = \\text{vol\\_persist\\_chg}_t \\times \\text{sign}(\\text{mom}_{20,t})</div>\n<h2>参数</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>参数</th><th>值</th><th>说明</th></tr><tr><td><code>RVOL_WINDOW</code></td><td><code>60</code></td><td>warm-up gate: realized vol</td></tr><tr><td><code>EWMA_LAMBDA</code></td><td><code>0.94</code></td><td>warm-up gate: EWMA vol</td></tr><tr><td><code>JUMP_THRESHOLD</code></td><td><code>3.0</code></td><td>warm-up gate: jump detection</td></tr><tr><td><code>JUMP_FREQ_WINDOW</code></td><td><code>60</code></td><td>warm-up gate: jump-freq rolling window</td></tr><tr><td><code>MOM_WINDOW</code></td><td><code>20</code></td><td>momentum lookback</td></tr><tr><td><code>VOL_PERSIST_SHIFT</code></td><td><code>20</code></td><td>cond_vol change-rate lookback</td></tr><tr><td><code>HOLD_DAYS</code></td><td><code>10</code></td><td>h10 variant</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>验证状态</h2>\n<ul><li>corr vs Polars: 1.0</li>\n<li>Pandas 运行时间: 13.85s</li>\n</ul>"}